s to give the Holy Spirit to His chil-</div><div class="t m1f9b xc5 he y146 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dren ? Luke 11:13. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
